data.description: Charming Home is a must see!  Recently reduced price. 3 bedrooms and 1 full bath. Large bedroom on main level and 2 additional bedrooms upstairs with a nice size loft and attic. Well maintained lawn. Home built in 1900 with lots of character and storage. Never run out of hot water with the Instant on Tankless water heater! Beautiful remodeled Kitchen. Laundry/mudroom opens to patio area and carport. This home is clean, well maintained and cozy. Close to downtown National Historic District with plenty of stores, restaurants, and other attractions nearby. Outdoor Grower's Market is just a few blocks away. This Home shows easily! Call/Text to set up a viewing time. Just 1 hour window needed.
data.whatILove: Come see for yourself! Call or Text 541-295-4591 to set up a viewing.
